(30, '2019-12-05 01:11:27', '2019-12-05 01:11:27', NULL, 31, 31, '<p>Berdasarkan hasil permintaan keterangan kepada Ketua Pokja II Ditjen P2P Sdr.&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\'>Asep Suryakusumah, SKM, MKM.&nbsp; bahwa</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\'>&nbsp;Pokja II menggagalkan lelang paket BTI dan Lavarsida\r\nsebanyak 2 kali melalui SPSE dikarenakan tidak ada peserta yang lulus evaluasi\r\nteknis.</span><p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\'>Perubahan spesifikasi Paket BTI :</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\'>1. Dilakukan rapat kajian antara Pokja, PPK, dan User setelah lelang\r\nBTI pertama gagal dan disepakati bahwa spesifikasi BTI berupa &acirc;&#128;&#156;harus teregistrasi\r\nWHOPES dan KOMPES&acirc;&#128;&#157; dihilangkan dan diganti dengan persyaratan bahwa harus\r\nteregistrasi di Kementerian Pertanian, persyaratan &acirc;&#128;&#156;uji toksisitas di Indonesia&acirc;&#128;&#157;\r\ndiubah hanya mensyaratkan &acirc;&#128;&#152;uji toksisitas&acirc;&#128;&#157;.<p></p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\'>\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\'>2.<span style=\'font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \"Times New Roman\";\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\'>Pada rapat kajian\r\nsetelah gagal lelang BTI kedua, spesifikasi BTI yang mensyaratkan ISO 9001:2008\r\ndihilangkan.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\'><p>Perubahan spesifikasi paket larvasida :</p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\'>1.<span style=\'font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \"Times New Roman\";\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\'>Pada saat lelang lavarsida\r\npertama gagal, spesifikasi terkait Larvasida WHOPES dan KOMPES dihilangkan,\r\nformulasi cairan atau granule dihilangkan. Karena BTI dan Larvasida merupakan\r\nbarang yang sama sehingga spesifikasi Larvasida disamakan dengan BTI dan\r\nditambahkan persyaratan ISO 9001:2008.<p></p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\'><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">2. Pada\r\nsaat lelang lavarsida kedua gagal, spesifikasi diubah yaitu persyaratan ISO\r\n9001:2008 dihilangkan dan masa kadaluarsa larvasida menjadi 18 bulan.</span><br></p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\'><p><br></p></span></p></p>\n', NULL, NULL, 57, NULL);
